Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:17.39,ED II Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}hametsu sae itowanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.81,0:22:34.95,ED II Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}imada kono te ni nokoru kakera datte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.49,0:22:44.58,ED II Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}anata no mono
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:51.13,ED II Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}nanimokamo nakushitemo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.46,0:22:55.30,ED II Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}sasageru mono ga aru no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.09,0:23:03.27,ED II Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}mirai datte inochi de sae
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.69,0:23:14.03,ED II Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}yaketsukita kanjou mo fumou na inori mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:19.74,ED II Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}sugaru buzama mo mitsugu oroka mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.74,0:23:25.45,ED II Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}yanda koe mo kegareta ryoote mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:35.55,ED II Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}kizu de fusagareta kokoro mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:17.39,ED II Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}破滅さえ厭わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.81,0:22:34.95,ED II Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}未だこの手に残る欠片だって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.49,0:22:44.58,ED II Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}あなたのもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:51.13,ED II Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}何もかも失くしても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.46,0:22:55.30,ED II Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}捧げるものがあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.09,0:23:03.27,ED II Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}未来だって　命でさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.69,0:23:14.03,ED II Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}焼け尽きた感情も　不毛な祈りも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:19.74,ED II Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}縋る無様も　見継ぐ愚かも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.74,0:23:25.45,ED II Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}病んだ声も　汚れた両手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:35.55,ED II Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}傷で塞がれた心も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:17.39,ED II BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}Não odeie a destruição também.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.81,0:22:34.95,ED II BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}Ei, até os pedaços que restam nestas mãos
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.49,0:22:44.58,ED II BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}pertencem a você.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:51.13,ED II BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}Mesmo que eu perca tudo,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.46,0:22:55.30,ED II BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}ainda tenho algo a oferecer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.09,0:23:03.27,ED II BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}Meu futuro, minha vida...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.69,0:23:14.03,ED II BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}Minhas emoções fervorosas, minhas orações infrutíferas,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:19.74,ED II BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}a feiura a qual me agarro, a tolice que forneço,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.74,0:23:25.45,ED II BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}minha voz insatisfeita, minhas mãos sujas,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:35.55,ED II BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}e meu coração, aberto pelas cicatrizes.
